metadata.name: LOVE LONDON
metadata.description:
Celebrating fashion and art in the magical city of London. From the architecture to the culture to the fashion to the accents that epitomised so beautifully.

An art collaboration of artists who believes in slow fashion and sustainability. Inspired by the British Fashion Brand MANIAC DESIGN LONDON

Art Director: Mani Saemi Motion: Meron Saemi 
Sound: Armyar
